    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed the CFD hemolysis prediction package for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under VAD conditions. Based on the overall evidence package, including Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification and bench-top validation data, the team concluded that the model provides sufficient credibility for the intended use and accepts the model for the stated COU. Several factors remain unassessed or below required levels, but the panel judged the overall evidence adequate.",
